text: Diana Gordon (born August 25, 1985), formerly known by her stage name Wynter, is an American singer-songwriter specializing in dance, house, and R&B.; She is signed to Atlantic Records and released her debut extended play in 2010. == References == Category:1990 births Category:African-American singers Category:American R&B; singers Category:Singer-songwriters from New York City Category:Atlantic Records artists Category:Living people
